OL,14,Gthere? (Have they always been here, in
OL,15,Gsecret?) This talk will cover the
OL,16,Ghistory of scanning things that
OL,17,Gcontain information such as the
OL,18,Gbarcode, covering not just one but TWO
OL,19,Gwhole dimensions of scanning. Where
